  "keyFeatures": [
    "Incremental time-series data synchronization via Pipes",
    "CLI tool (`mrsm`) for managing all data operations",
    "Python API for programmatic pipe management",
    "Plugin system to ingest any data source with a simple fetch function",
    "Multi-connector support: SQL, API, ValKey, and custom connectors",
    "Built-in web API using FastAPI/uvicorn for serving data",
    "Docker stack with TimescaleDB and Grafana for instant visualization",
    "Background jobs and systemd integration for scheduled syncing",
    "Compose projects for declarative pipeline configuration",
    "Virtual environment management for plugin dependencies"
  ],
